  <summary date="2022-01-03T16:51:22Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Stop Tip-overs of Unstable, Risky Dressers on Youth Act or the STURDY ActThis bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to revise the safety standards for freestanding clothing storage units such as dressers, bureaus, or chests of drawers. Such standards must include specified testing related to tip overs and new warning requirements&#160;for all such products entering the U.S. market.</summary>
